{
  "stem": "13469.3",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the monies, shares, jewelry, everything, we had to hand over to this bank, Lippmann, Rosenthal kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we never saw it again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were many of these laws in there, we had, going through my notes kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember them all, but other people will remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we're now in 1942 when they started deporting people from Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, it was done on a voluntary basis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were invited to volunteer to work for the Germans in camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And no doubt, there were certain incentives whereby they would be treated well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would be fed and everything else, if they volunteered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, obviously, not many people volunteered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then it became compulsory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And first of all, they had lists.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the Judenrat had to produce lists.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans would say, this week we want 5,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Judenrat then had the very difficult task of deciding which 5,000 Jews that lived in Amsterdam had to be deported.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I didn't know he worked for the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, again, Richie remembers it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, we have this list of all these documents where we have a letter to say that he was an inspector working for the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We believe that he worked in the financial department.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He helped the Jews to fill in the forms for handing over all their stuff to Lippmann, Rosenthal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lippmann, Rosenthal was a bank.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was a bank man, so he understood how to fill in the forms and whereby they had to transfer all their shares and any other kind of documents that they had to Lippmann, Rosenthal.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we believe he helped them with doing that job.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was what he did at the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
